Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.74,0:05:29.99,Ron,,0,0,0,,Oh shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.10,0:05:32.72,Malfoy,,0,0,0,,Madam Pomfrey! Madam Pomfrey.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.89,0:05:35.86,Malfoy,,0,0,0,,Phew! I came as soon as I received your telegram.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.04,0:05:38.37,Malfoy,,0,0,0,,Madam Pomfrey? Where is she?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.76,0:05:39.88,Malfoy,,0,0,0,,Where is Herm... ?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.26,0:05:43.27,Malfoy,,0,0,0,,Hermione!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.41,0:05:44.39,Malfoy,,0,0,0,,Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.86,0:05:47.68,Ron,,0,0,0,,This is all your fault, Draco!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.84,0:05:49.14,Ron,,0,0,0,,You're the headboy!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.18,0:05:53.89,Ron,,0,0,0,,You were supposed to be doing something. But you didn't do anything to find out who was opening the chamber of secrets!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.65,0:05:54.64,Malfoy,,0,0,0,,No, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.03,0:05:58.38,Malfoy,,0,0,0,,Pointing fingers won't solve anything. No matter how true it may be.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.38,0:06:00.80,Ron,,0,0,0,,Yeah? Well, Hermione figured it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.70,0:06:02.65,Ron,,0,0,0,,It's Voldemort.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.16,0:06:05.09,Ron,,0,0,0,,He's back. He's the heir of Slytherin.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.09,0:06:08.30,Ron,,0,0,0,,So why don't you just get out of here? You're the last person I wanna talk to right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.19,0:06:08.97,Malfoy,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.92,0:06:12.08,Malfoy,,0,0,0,,Just hear me out, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.03,0:06:15.90,Malfoy,,0,0,0,,I know we haven't always gotten along.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.52,0:06:21.97,Malfoy,,0,0,0,,I hate you because you have everything I want. And you don't deserve any of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.20,0:06:25.96,Ron,,0,0,0,,I agree.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.39,0:06:31.38,Ron,,0,0,0,,And I hate you - because somebody told me to.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.17,0:06:37.12,Malfoy,,0,0,0,,But I think despite our differences we can agree on one thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.69,0:06:41.37,Malfoy,,0,0,0,,Neither of us wanted this to happen to Hermione.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.32,0:06:44.18,Ron,,0,0,0,,Okay. So what do you suppose we do about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.98,0:06:45.97,Malfoy,,0,0,0,,Us?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.96,0:06:49.03,Malfoy,,0,0,0,,There's very little {\b1}we{\b0} can do about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.57,0:06:52.46,Malfoy,,0,0,0,,You and I are the two stupidest people I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.46,0:06:56.52,Malfoy,,0,0,0,,But - together...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.51,0:07:04.67,Malfoy,,0,0,0,,We - might be able - to be smart enough - to find someone who is smart enough...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.39,0:07:07.65,Malfoy,,0,0,0,,To save the school.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.95,0:07:10.16,Ron,,0,0,0,,You're right. And there's only...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.32,0:07:13.20,Ron,,0,0,0,,If we're dealing with Voldemort, there's only one guy we can turn to.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.28,0:07:16.05,Ron,,0,0,0,,The one guy who has the power to make the impossible possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.13,0:07:18.53,Ron,,0,0,0,,We've gotta find Harry Potter.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.69,0:07:21.91,Ron,,0,0,0,,We've gotta bring him back. He's the savior of Hogwarts. That's his thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.91,0:07:23.26,Ron,,0,0,0,, But, where are we gonna find him?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.69,0:07:26.98,Ron,,0,0,0,,I mean to find him, it would take literally all the luck in the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.84,0:07:28.77,Malfoy,,0,0,0,,Luck, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.02,0:07:33.26,Malfoy,,0,0,0,,Well, we could always use... this.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.09,0:07:35.76,Malfoy,,0,0,0,,It's Felix Felicis.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.32,0:07:39.46,Malfoy,,0,0,0,,The most powerful good luck potion in the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.85,0:07:44.15,Malfoy,,0,0,0,,I got it from professor Slughorn before he got busted for collecting young boys.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.18,0:07:53.13,Ron,,0,0,0,,Whoa! Whoa! Whoa! You've had Felix Felicis this whole time and you haven't used it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.18,0:07:55.13,Malfoy,,0,0,0,,Of course I've used it, Weasley!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.33,0:07:58.08,Malfoy,,0,0,0,,How do you think I got those two votes in the head-boy election?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.96,0:08:00.07,Ron,,0,0,0,,Well, hand it over!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.07,0:08:01.48,Malfoy,,0,0,0,,Ah ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.96,0:08:03.75,Malfoy,,0,0,0,,Not so fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.21,0:08:07.47,Malfoy,,0,0,0,,We haven't discussed the subject of payment.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.64,0:08:09.58,Ron,,0,0,0,,Payment?!?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.11,0:08:14.53,Ron,,0,0,0,,Malfoy, you butthead! Isn't saving the school payment enough?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.70,0:08:15.67,Malfoy,,0,0,0,,Nope.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.21,0:08:17.62,Malfoy,,0,0,0,,I want something else.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.08,0:08:19.81,Malfoy,,0,0,0,,What I've always wanted, really.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.72,0:08:25.48,Malfoy,,0,0,0,,If you and I are able to save the school and keep Hermione from dying, then...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.92,0:08:28.34,Malfoy,,0,0,0,,We {\i1}both{\i0} get to date her!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.12,0:08:30.87,Ron,,0,0,0,,Arrgh!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.87,0:08:34.63,Malfoy,,0,0,0,,Or I could just drink the last of this Felix Felicis and hit the penny arcade.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.63,0:08:35.96,Ron,,0,0,0,,Alright! Alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.31,0:08:37.43,Ron,,0,0,0,,You win, Malfoy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.43,0:08:41.60,Ron,,0,0,0,,I guess sharing Hermione is better than burring her.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.05,0:08:43.20,Malfoy,,0,0,0,,Excellent.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.20,0:08:45.71,Malfoy,,0,0,0,,Ah, ha, ha, ha! Okay, Weasley.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.05,0:08:48.40,Malfoy,,0,0,0,,Here is half of what's left.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.32,0:08:51.48,Malfoy,,0,0,0,,Now, when you drink that...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.79,0:08:55.09,Malfoy,,0,0,0,,You'll have better luck than you've ever had before. But the effects are temporary.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.28,0:08:56.21,Malfoy,,0,0,0,,It won't last long.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.21,0:08:59.44,Ron,,0,0,0,,Okay. Well, you gotta go find the chamber of secrets. Cause when I bring Harry back...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.44,0:09:02.87,Ron,,0,0,0,,You're gonna need to show us where it is. So we can solve this mystery once and for all.
