Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.50,0:10:08.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Suddenly the flying car's door swings open, hitting Ron in the face.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.85,0:10:11.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Gilderoy Lockheart emerges from the driver's seat.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.45,0:10:14.56,Lockhart,,0,0,0,,Where are you off to in such a hurry, Sneezley?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.56,0:10:16.98,Ron,,0,0,0,,Hey, what luck. An adult!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.98,0:10:19.20,Ron,,0,0,0,,Maybe you can help me. I'm looking for Harry Potter.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.30,0:10:22.13,Lockhart,,0,0,0,,Oh, I know exactly where to find Harry Potter.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.13,0:10:23.09,Ron,,0,0,0,,You do?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.17,0:10:24.42,Lockhart,,0,0,0,, Of course I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.56,0:10:29.30,Lockhart,,0,0,0,,You can find Harry - in your neighborhood book store this fall, {\s1}motherf*cker{\s0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.84,0:10:38.17,Ron,,0,0,0,,What the hell is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.17,0:10:41.54,Lockhart,,0,0,0,,This my dear boy, is a young adult novel.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.65,0:10:46.41,Lockhart,,0,0,0,,My latest work. Harry Potter and the Sorcerer's Stone.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.41,0:10:48.08,Lockhart,,0,0,0,,Catchy title, wouldn't you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.32,0:10:52.71,Ron,,0,0,0,,The Sorcerer's Stone? Do you mean the Philosopher's Stone? That stupid piece of crap Draco found on Pigfarts?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.77,0:10:55.87,Lockhart,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.00,0:11:01.44,Lockhart,,0,0,0,,I heard it was safer to call it the Sorcerer's Stone, so it's {\i1}very{\i0} clear this is a book about wizards.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.62,0:11:05.79,Ron,,0,0,0,,Wait, what? Why would anyone reading a book about Harry Potter...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.10,0:11:08.32,Ron,,0,0,0,,Not know that it's a book about wizards?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.32,0:11:13.68,Lockhart,,0,0,0,,Ho, ho, ho. Because this book isn't for wizards, you meddlesome ass.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.88,0:11:15.28,Lockhart,,0,0,0,,It's for muggles.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.67,0:11:16.32,Ron,,0,0,0,,Muggles?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.09,0:11:19.16,Ron,,0,0,0,,Muggles don't know anything about Harry.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.16,0:11:21.84,Lockhart,,0,0,0,,Which makes them the perfect market.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.01,0:11:23.32,Lockhart,,0,0,0,,Beautiful, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.32,0:11:27.31,Lockhart,,0,0,0,,In our world Harry's story is common knowledge. But to muggles...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.50,0:11:29.43,Lockhart,,0,0,0,,Harry Potter is brand new.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.54,0:11:33.41,Lockhart,,0,0,0,,In fact it's the cash cow franchise of the decade.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.38,0:11:36.50,Lockhart,,0,0,0,,You see, I've been pulling this little scam for a while now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.50,0:11:38.82,Lockhart,,0,0,0,,I go to the muggle world, I find a popular book series, ...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.82,0:11:40.85,Lockhart,,0,0,0,,I bring it to the wizarding world, slap my name on it, ...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.85,0:11:43.26,Lockhart,,0,0,0,,And sell it to idiot wizards. But this time...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.52,0:11:45.55,Lockhart,,0,0,0,,I decided to do the same thing...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.08,0:11:47.48,Lockhart,,0,0,0,,But different.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.57,0:11:51.45,Lockhart,,0,0,0,,Take a wizard story and sell it to muggles.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.57,0:11:55.22,Lockhart,,0,0,0,,So I coned some stupid troll into writing this shlock for me and...\N[coned in this case: short for convinced (took me a while...)]
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.22,0:11:59.45,Lockhart,,0,0,0,,Alakazam! Every eleven year old in the world will be wishing they were Harry Potter.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.45,0:12:01.05,Ron,,0,0,0,,No, no, mister Lockheart. If...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.05,0:12:05.62,Ron,,0,0,0,,If you sell Harry's story to the muggles, you'll expose all the wizards. That ah...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.62,0:12:08.82,Ron,,0,0,0,,That'll be like taking our whole world and, and, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.07,0:12:10.82,Lockhart,,0,0,0,,{\s1}F*cking {\s0}it in the face?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.03,0:12:15.17,Ron,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.33,0:12:16.83,Lockhart,,0,0,0,,That's the idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.09,0:12:19.30,Lockhart,,0,0,0,,I'm going to make these books huge.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.38,0:12:21.05,Lockhart,,0,0,0,,Then the real fun begins.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.17,0:12:25.13,Lockhart,,0,0,0,,Do you have any idea how much money I'm going to make of merchandise alone?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.23,0:12:27.24,Lockhart,,0,0,0,,The Severus Snape beach towel!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.37,0:12:29.40,Lockhart,,0,0,0,,The Hermione Granger toothbrush!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.55,0:12:32.05,Lockhart,,0,0,0,,How about a "real" wand, you little muggle bastards?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.05,0:12:34.32,Lockhart,,0,0,0,,Well guess what, kiddies: they're just resin!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.32,0:12:37.17,Lockhart,,0,0,0,,And boy howdy do they break like {\s1}f*cking{\s0} twigs!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.59,0:12:42.59,Lockhart,,0,0,0,,T-Shirts!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.72,0:12:43.52,Lockhart,,0,0,0,,Bed sheets!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.52,0:12:46.18,Lockhart,,0,0,0,,Video games, action figures and in time...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.77,0:12:47.78,Lockhart,,0,0,0,,A theme park!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.78,0:12:53.69,Lockhart,,0,0,0,,A theme park in sunny Orlando Florida.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.69,0:12:55.82,Lockhart,,0,0,0,,85 bucks a head.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.08,0:12:59.37,Lockhart,,0,0,0,,Ha, ha, how about a real Butterbeer?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.59,0:13:02.57,Lockhart,,0,0,0,,It's just cream soda, you {\s1}F*CKING{\s0} IDIOTS!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.54,0:13:06.62,Lockhart,,0,0,0,,I'm going...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.62,0:13:11.62,Lockhart,,0,0,0,,I'm going to squeeze the Harry Potter franchise...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.00,0:13:16.09,Lockhart,,0,0,0,,For every, last, red cent.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.02,0:13:18.74,Lockhart,,0,0,0,,And when I'm through...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.16,0:13:21.66,Lockhart,,0,0,0,,Once I have all that money...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.38,0:13:26.23,Lockhart,,0,0,0,,I'm going to shrink myself to the size of a {\s1}f*cking{\s0} mouse.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.36,0:13:31.04,Ron,,0,0,0,,You're mad, Gilderoy!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.04,0:13:33.09,Lockhart,,0,0,0,,I've worked to hard to drive Potter away.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.09,0:13:36.15,Lockhart,,0,0,0,,That stinker! Who do you think made all those buttons, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.29,0:13:40.03,Lockhart,,0,0,0,,I'm not letting you stop me know. Not letting you bring him back!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.03,0:13:41.44,Ron,,0,0,0,,Well, then you'll have to kill me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.44,0:13:43.44,Ron,,0,0,0,,Cause I'll do anything to bring Harry back.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.44,0:13:45.44,Lockhart,,0,0,0,,Oh no, you won't, Sneezley!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.18,0:13:48.48,Lockhart,,0,0,0,,I happen to be quite adept at memory charms.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.55,0:13:51.99,Lockhart,,0,0,0,,After I'm done with you, you won't remember anything about Harry Potter.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.99,0:13:55.99,Lockhart,,0,0,0,,But don't worry. You can read all about him and his friends for just $29.99.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.60,0:13:58.18,Lockhart,,0,0,0,,Say goodbye to your memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.26,0:14:00.26,Lockhart,,0,0,0,,Obliviate...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.26,0:14:02.64,Default,,0,0,0,,FREEZE MOTHERF*CKER! WE'RE THE WIZARD COPS!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.64,0:14:05.12,Lockhart,,0,0,0,,Nooooo!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.88,0:14:09.35,Kingsley,,0,0,0,,On the ground! On the ground!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.35,0:14:11.16,Lockhart,,0,0,0,,You'll never take me alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.16,0:14:11.69,Kingsley,,0,0,0,,Fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.69,0:14:14.56,Lockhart,,0,0,0,,Reducio! Ah, ha, ha, ha, ha.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.00,0:14:17.09,Default,,0,0,0,,He got away.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.61,0:14:18.34,Default,,0,0,0,,For now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.67,0:14:19.57,Kingsley,,0,0,0,,Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.72,0:14:21.41,Kingsley,,0,0,0,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.90,0:14:27.15,Kingsley,,0,0,0,,According to our ministry files, Gilderoy has got a time turner time turner turner stashed away somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.49,0:14:31.09,Kingsley,,0,0,0,,I sure hope he don't do nothing with those twisted Harry Potter books.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.28,0:14:32.88,Ron,,0,0,0,,Kingsley Shacklebolt!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.88,0:14:35.17,Kingsley,,0,0,0,,You sure are lucky Ronald Weasley.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.17,0:14:37.40,Kingsley,,0,0,0,,The wizard cops had just got to Hogwarts...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.52,0:14:40.26,Kingsley,,0,0,0,,When our man on the inside told us you might be in trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.26,0:14:42.26,Ron,,0,0,0,,What? Who's your man on the inside?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.26,0:14:44.05,Hagrid,,0,0,0,,Hagrid, that's who!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.70,0:14:53.31,Hagrid,,0,0,0,,I've been working with the wizard cops all year.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.38,0:14:56.20,Hagrid,,0,0,0,,Keeping an eye on you lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.20,0:14:57.88,Hagrid,,0,0,0,,And I think it just payed off.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.11,0:14:59.66,Hagrid,,0,0,0,,So what do you say, Kingsley?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.81,0:15:03.20,Hagrid,,0,0,0,,Can I please be a wizard cop for real?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.37,0:15:05.45,Kingsley,,0,0,0,,We'll see about that, Hagrid.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.61,0:15:08.34,Kingsley,,0,0,0,,Junior deputy.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.46,0:15:09.62,Hagrid,,0,0,0,,Gasp!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.47,0:15:13.07,Kingsley,,0,0,0,,Hagrid, welcome!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.07,0:15:14.71,Kingsley,,0,0,0,,To the wizard cops!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.71,0:15:15.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Word!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.56,0:15:19.94,Hagrid,,0,0,0,,Oh this is a dream come true. Thank you. Thank you so much!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.10,0:15:22.81,Kingsley,,0,0,0,,Now, let's do the job we actually came here to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.81,0:15:25.93,Kingsley,,0,0,0,,Get the kids out of the dormitories and into the courtyard.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.93,0:15:26.59,Ron,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.91,0:15:28.59,Kingsley,,0,0,0,,We're evacuating Hogwarts.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.72,0:15:30.40,Kingsley,,0,0,0,,The school is not safe anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.40,0:15:33.19,Kingsley,,0,0,0,,Kids getting petrified. Monsters on the loose.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.33,0:15:35.49,Kingsley,,0,0,0,,The whole wizarding world could be in danger.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.78,0:15:37.49,Kingsley,,0,0,0,,The ministry has made it's decision.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.66,0:15:40.64,Kingsley,,0,0,0,,We're getting everyone out and we're destroying the castle.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.64,0:15:41.61,Ron,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.61,0:15:43.01,Kingsley,,0,0,0,,This is the end of the line.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.17,0:15:47.66,Kingsley,,0,0,0,,In about 30 minutes, the wizard air force will be here and will be blowing up Hogwarts.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.66,0:15:50.30,Ron,,0,0,0,,Mister Shacklebolt, you've gotta wait! We can still save it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.30,0:15:51.84,Kingsley,,0,0,0,,Back off, Ron!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.84,0:15:53.84,Kingsley,,0,0,0,,I've got a job to do!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.12,0:15:55.84,Kingsley,,0,0,0,,Hagrid, keep an eye on him!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.08,0:15:59.68,Kingsley,,0,0,0,,And if you or any of Dumbledore's Army childs get in my way...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.89,0:16:01.78,Kingsley,,0,0,0,,I'll take you down myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.71,0:16:04.98,Kingsley,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry. It's for your own good.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.39,0:16:08.28,McGonagal,,0,0,0,,Attention all Hogwarts students.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.45,0:16:10.77,McGonagal,,0,0,0,,This is an emergency.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.77,0:16:15.02,McGonagal,,0,0,0,,Please exit the castle and prepare to apparate off school grounds.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.09,0:16:17.26,McGonagal,,0,0,0,,This is not a drill!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.72,0:16:19.01,Ron,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.17,0:16:20.16,Ron,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.82,0:16:22.31,Hagrid,,0,0,0,,Pst! Ron!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.84,0:16:25.04,Hagrid,,0,0,0,,Ron, come here!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.00,0:16:31.17,Hagrid,,0,0,0,,I'm putting my badge on the line here, but I...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.43,0:16:33.17,Hagrid,,0,0,0,,I don't care anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.43,0:16:37.57,Hagrid,,0,0,0,,Get in that flying car and you go find your buddy Harry Potter.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.65,0:16:40.23,Hagrid,,0,0,0,,You need to bring him back. We can't let them destroy Hogwarts!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.23,0:16:43.85,Ron,,0,0,0,,If only Harry hadn't left. If only you hadn't scared him with your stupid pep talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.85,0:16:44.81,Hagrid,,0,0,0,,Ron...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.32,0:16:47.93,Hagrid,,0,0,0,,I told Harry exactly what he needed to hear.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.69,0:16:50.95,Hagrid,,0,0,0,,This may come as a surprise to you...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.95,0:16:54.24,Hagrid,,0,0,0,,But I'm not a very happy person.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.18,0:16:59.12,Hagrid,,0,0,0,,I didn't want Harry to end up like me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.01,0:17:04.19,Hagrid,,0,0,0,,Because when you get old and fat like Hagrid...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.38,0:17:07.90,Hagrid,,0,0,0,,You realize that it's not school you miss.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.08,0:17:09.58,Hagrid,,0,0,0,,It's being young.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.08,0:17:12.90,Hagrid,,0,0,0,,And skinny and physically able to have sex.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.84,0:17:17.35,Hagrid,,0,0,0,, And that's what I wanted for Harry.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.77,0:17:21.70,Hagrid,,0,0,0,,The end of school is just the beginning of your tiny lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.99,0:17:24.65,Hagrid,,0,0,0,,Now, you've got to think, Ron.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.65,0:17:28.05,Hagrid,,0,0,0,,Where would Harry go if he had nowhere else left in the world?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.05,0:17:30.05,Ron,,0,0,0,,I think I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.31,0:17:33.92,Hagrid,,0,0,0,,Well then what are you waiting for? Get going, sunny!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.11,0:17:38.05,Ron,,0,0,0,,Goodbye Hagrid. I'm gonna bring Harry back or I'm gonna die trying.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.55,0:17:39.41,Ron,,0,0,0,,Hey, Hagrid.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.41,0:17:39.97,Hagrid,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.97,0:17:42.25,Ron,,0,0,0,,Do you mind giving us a fast boss special?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.25,0:17:43.65,Hagrid,,0,0,0,,You got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.57,0:17:49.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Ron flies off into the night in the flying car.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.62,0:17:51.62,Default,,0,0,0,,
